    "title": "Starfield Update 1.16.236 – April 7, 2026",
    "preview_text": "The Free Lanes update is Starfield’s biggest update yet! Now available on all platforms, it adds the ability to fly between planets within a star system, improvements to ships and outposts, a new",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFUDRmSWwAA7s2f.jpg",
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 408
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "eq70s",
          "text": "The Free Lanes update is Starfield’s biggest update yet! Now available on all platforms, it adds the ability to fly between planets within a star system, improvements to ships and outposts, a new Quantum Entanglement Device to transfer items when going through the Unity, the new X-Tech for better customization, the new Anchorpoint Station, and many more fixes and improvements. Learn more about the update here and read on for the full update notes.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 12,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "40hri",
          "text": "Update Notes",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "4e1mm",
          "text": "Features",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "et334",
          "text": "Free Lanes: The player can now use cruise mode to travel in open space or to POI locations between planets inside a star system.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2rhim",
          "text": "Added X-Tech crafting support to Weapons and Armor. This allows players to further customize the legendary effects on their equipment.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "eao1v",
          "text": "Added Additional Quality Tiers to weapons and suits.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "d7fpn",
          "text": "Added Rank 4 Legendary effects for weapons and suits.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "633qm",
          "text": "Added Upgrade modules. These can be installed to improve one attribute of a weapon or Suit.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "abnmr",
          "text": "Added New weapon skins that can be applied to select weapons at a workbench.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2kk9p",
          "text": "Added a buildable ship optimization terminal. The player can spend X-Tech to improve several attributes of their ship.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c96a6",
          "text": "Added Ship Equipment schematics. This new equipment can be added in the ship builder after it is discovered.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "75ur4",
          "text": "Added Legendary Enemy Modifiers. Legendary enemies can now appear with new modifiers that make them more challenging.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "a32vg",
          "text": "Added Legendary Enemy Modifiers settings into Gameplay Options, so players can adjust when they start appearing.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "a01uh",
          "text": "Added Quantum Entanglement Device. This gives players the ability to transfer some items when they choose to go through the Unity.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3o68k",
          "text": "Starborn Powers can now be upgraded with Quantum Essence.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4upor",
          "text": "Quantum Essence can now be added to the Favorites menu to for quick access.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9lfsf",
          "text": "Starborn ships now reward the player with Quantum Essence when destroyed.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "e6spj",
          "text": "Added the Database menu which allows for better location, resource, and recipe tracking based on character’s knowledge of the Settled Systems.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bf4cr",
          "text": "Added Outpost Quality of life improvements such as a Shared Outpost Container (allowing players to house and access inventory from various outpost locations), Production Rate information, and a more precise placement mode.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fnm0q",
          "text": "New vehicle: Moon Jumper.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "b0srt",
          "text": "Added new Player House - “Château des Étoiles”.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "aaovu",
          "text": "Added Colony Wars Action Heroes which provide benefits when found.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3ubpo",
          "text": "Added Colony War Action Heroes display cases as buildable objects.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4k049",
          "text": "Muria Siarkiewicz is now available to join player crew.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6uv80",
          "text": "Added an additional 3rd person Ship Camera distance that allows more of the ship to be visible.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3brk9",
          "text": "Added Always Show Landing Camera setting for those who want to see their ship land at known locations.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6apk2",
          "text": "Added Anchorpoint Station, a new POI that can be found in the Algorab system.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "79fc2",
          "text": "Added New Dungeons, Space Encounters, and Points of Interest throughout the game.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9smnb",
          "text": "Adjusted the distribution and cooldown timers for placement of points of interest on Planets.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9haar",
          "text": "Added additional photomode poses for the Rev-8.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "56gel",
          "text": "Terran Armada DLC Now Available.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 7,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "5vlsl",
          "text": "General",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "cffue",
          "text": "Steam - Disabled DLC will no longer re-install when launching the game.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dusu0",
          "text": "General crash and stability fixes.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "6a10i",
          "text": "Gameplay",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c2dtp",
          "text": "Improved loot found in containers with Expert and Master level locks.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1a7uv",
          "text": "Reactive Equipment - Resolved an issue with the sound effects for the Reactive legendary effect.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "26hhq",
          "text": "Addressed an issue that could cause NPCs to calculate weapon damage inconsistently.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dieij",
          "text": "Fixed an issue with CombaTech magazine accuracy bonuses not applying consistently.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8lik6",
          "text": "The player can now jump while reloading the XM-2311, Old Earth Pistol, and Livingstone's Pistol.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3m4tu",
          "text": "Bounty targets in cities should now be properly interactable.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ajo79",
          "text": "Resolved an issue that could potentially cause non-combat background music to no longer play.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "57aul",
          "text": "Photo Mode - Addressed an issue that could cause issues when entering photomode while also entering an interior.",
